<HEADLINE>
FT  26 MAY 93 / London Stock Exchange: New highs and lows for 1993
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By CHRISTOPHER PRICE, STEVE THOMPSON and PETER JOHN
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
NEW HIGHS (152).
BANKS (6) Abbey Natl., Natl. Australia, Ryl. Bk. Scotland, Sakura, Sanwa,
Sumitomo, BLDG MATLS (7) BMSS, Brit. Dredging, Lilleshall, Do 9pc Prf., RMC,
Wolseley, BUSINESS SERVS (3) Hutchison Whmp., Page (M), Securiguard, CHEMS
(1) Hartons, CONGLOMERATES (3) Jardine, Trafalgar Hse., Do A, CONTG &amp;
