<HEADLINE>
FT  26 MAY 93 / Commodities and Agriculture: Minor metals prices
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Prices from Metal Bulletin (last week's in brackets).
ANTIMONY: European free market 99.6 per cent, Dollars per tonne, in
