</XX>
<IN>P4911 Electric Services.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>RES  Energy use.
    CMMT  Comment &amp; Analysis.
    TECH  Services &amp; Services use.
</TP>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
